# German Learning – Word Extraction

## Context

Project is for learning German at B1 level. User writes texts in `readle/`, AI extracts words and distributes them to `vocabulary/` by type.

## Text File Naming Format

New texts in `readle/` use format: **`Y-m-d_H:i_title.md`**

Example: `2025-03-10_14:30_mein-tag.md` (date_time_title)

## Text Content Format in readle/

When user says "create new text" and gives a title, create **empty file** with only:

```markdown
# [Title]

[Y-m-d]
```

No additional content – user writes the text themselves.

All `.md` files in `readle/` must follow this format (title + date).

## Translation Format in readle/

When adding translations to a text, use this format per sentence:

```
[DE] {German}
[SR] {Serbian}
[EN] {English}

```

Empty line between each block. Order: German, Serbian, English.

## Consolidated German Text at End

**Always** add at the end of the text file, after corrections, extraction, and translations:

```markdown
## {title}

{All German sentences as one continuous paragraph}
```

Format: `## {title}` (from the main heading) followed by the full German text without [DE] tags.

## Word Type Mapping

| German type | File | Examples |
|-------------|------|----------|
| Substantiv | vocabulary/Substantive.md | die Arbeit, der Tag |
| Verb | vocabulary/Verben.md | gehen, lesen |
| Adjektiv | vocabulary/Adjektive.md | freundlich, wichtig |
| Adverb | vocabulary/Adverbien.md | sehr, oft |
| Präposition | vocabulary/Präpositionen.md | in, auf, mit |
| Konjunktion, Partikel | vocabulary/Andere.md | und, aber |
| Pronomen (zamenice) | vocabulary/Zamenice.md | ich, du, dein – po tipu (lične, posedovne, upitne…) |

**No subfolders** – one file per type.

## Vocabulary File Format

One file per type. Words sorted alphabetically (ABC). Format per word:

```markdown
# [Type]

## {word}

[sr] {Serbian translation}
[en] {English translation}

```

- **Substantive**: heading with article – `## der Arbeit`, `## die Kunst`, `## das Jahr`
- **Verben**: infinitive only. Each verb has links to its forms in `vremena/` (Präsens, Perfekt, Präteritum, Plusquamperfekt, Futur I, Futur II).
- **Translations**: [sr] Serbian, [en] English
- **Sort**: words alphabetically (ABC)
- Empty line between each word block
- Do not duplicate words – check existing files before adding

## B1 Level

B1 covers ~2500–3000 words: everyday life, work, health, travel, education. Skip A1/A2 basic words (ich, und, ist) unless contextually important.

## Vremena (Verb Tenses)

Folder `vremena/` contains B1 tenses: Präsens, Perfekt, Präteritum, Plusquamperfekt, Futur-I, Futur-II.

**Pravilo**: U svakom fajlu u `vremena/` moraju biti **svi** glagoli iz `vocabulary/Verben.md` – sa konjugacijom u tom vremenu, prevodom [sr]/[en] i linkom na infinitiv `[→ verb](vocabulary/Verben.md#verb)`.

**Format u vremenima** (po glagolu):
```markdown
## {infinitive}

{konjugacija: ich, du, er/sie/es, wir, ihr, sie}

[sr] {prevod}
[en] {prevod}

[→ {infinitive}](../vocabulary/Verben.md#{anchor})
```

**Themen** – fajlovi u `themen/*/` (alltag/, grammatik/, itd.): link na vocabulary mora biti `../../vocabulary/` (dva nivoa gore).

Prazan red: (1) između oblika i prevoda, (2) između prevoda i linka nazad.

**Format u Verben.md** (za svaki glagol, posle [en]):
```markdown

[Präsens](../vremena/Präsens.md#verb) · [Perfekt](../vremena/Perfekt.md#verb) · [Präteritum](../vremena/Präteritum.md#verb) · [Plusquamperfekt](../vremena/Plusquamperfekt.md#verb) · [Futur I](../vremena/Futur-I.md#verb) · [Futur II](../vremena/Futur-II.md#verb)
```

Anchor za `sich anfühlen`: `#sich-anfühlen` (razmak → crtica).

## Link verification – obavezno

**Svaki link koji agent postavi mora biti proveren pre finalizacije.**

- Proveri putanju (relativna od izvornog fajla)
- Proveri anchor (slug naslova: razmaci→crtica, umlauti mogu varirati po rendereru)
- Testiraj: Cmd/Ctrl+click u editoru – link mora otvoriti tačan fajl i scroll do naslova
